Please implement this as a single pass parser.  it will be simpler and more efficient, and it becomes much easier to define how things like negative numbers and overflow will work.  Pseudocode is below.

value = 0;
loop over character in fmt:
    if !isdigit(character)
        if (character != postfix)
            return error
        return value
    new = value * 10 + character - '0'
    if new < value
         return error;  // overflow
    value = new;

return error

